VGanesha-The Source of LightSwathi Soft SolutionsBook-CD package (Price Rs.350)CD (without booklet) (Price Rs.150)Ganesha &#8211; The source of light,&#8217; is a &#8216;Book&#8211;CD&#8217; package published by Swathi Soft Solutions. The hybrid-CD has a video presentation of various images of Lord Ganesa captured imaginatively by photographer B.R.S.Sreenag. He has used the light and shade technique effectively to portray the Lord whose worship is believed to dispel darkness in life.Ganesa Gayathri, Ganesa Pancharatnam and excerpts from other popular Ganesa sthuthis in vogue, Ganesa Namavali, portions of Ganapthi Atharva Shiirshham (from Atharva Veda) have all been recited by P.C.Ramakrishna followed by its transliteration with his inimitable voice. The book is a helpful tool with all the above text falling in the same order as found in the audio.Archana Ram Kumar and B.R.Ramkumar take credits for the selection of the slokas and general research while Geeta Sundararajan has done the translation. The CD has 48 computer wallpapers, mobile phone wallpapers and computer screensavers comprising the images of Ganesa shown in the video.
